Privacy Policy
Latest update: Mar 31, 2022

Our privacy policy applies to information we collect when you use our applications. We may change this privacy policy from time to time. Whenever we make changes to this privacy policy, the changes are effective immediately after we post the updated privacy policy (as indicated at the top of our privacy policy). We encourage you to review our privacy policy whenever you access our services to stay informed about our information practices and the ways you can help protect your privacy.


* Information we collect from you

We don't store any personal data at all. Data used in sync services remain private to users and connected directly with the services and users. Sync services that could be used on our apps are iCloud by Apple and Dropbox varying on the apps.



* Third Party Service Providers

To provide you with the best services possible, we also use third party service providers, which we entrust storing data, its collection and analysis. Data collected are anonymous usage data including crash reports. We believe that all third party service providers are important to our effective operation. They have their own Privacy Policies and their own conditions, whether to collect your data or opt-out from it.

We provide the information on below service and you may check link to their respective Privacy Policy:

Google Firebase: https://policies.google.com/privacy
Microsoft Visual Studio App Center: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/appcenter/gdpr/


* Contact

If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at: contact@hahaint.com